    <div class="container">
        <p>Last updated: February 2026</p>

        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>Graviton is a motion-based game developed by Tsook Nir LTD. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how the app handles information.</p>

        <h2>Data We Do Not Collect</h2>
        <p>Graviton does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not use analytics, advertising, or tracking of any kind.</p>

        <h2>Motion Sensors</h2>
        <p>Graviton uses your device's motion sensors (gyroscope and accelerometer) to control gameplay. This data is used exclusively on your device in real time and is never stored or transmitted.</p>

        <h2>Local Storage</h2>
        <p>The app stores your game settings and best times locally on your device only. This data never leaves your device.</p>

        <h2>Third Parties</h2>
        <p>Graviton does not integrate any third-party SDKs, analytics tools, or advertising networks.</p>

        <h2>Children</h2>
        <p>Graviton does not collect any data from any users, including children under the age of 13.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:support@tsook.net" style="color:#f0c040;">support@tsook.net</a></p>
